#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Units"
msgstr "Jedinice"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose the default unit that will be used in your slides."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite podrazumijevanu jedinicu koja će biti korištena u slajdovima."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handle radius"
msgstr "Drške radijusa"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select a shape with the default tool (arrow) you see the yellow and "
"red rectangles. These are called handles (used for resizing, rotation, ...). "
"The handle radius changes the size of the handles. If you make them bigger "
"it is easier to hit them."
msgstr ""
"Ako izaberete oblik sa zadanim alatom (strijela) možete vidjeti žute i "
"crvene pravougaonike. Oni se zovu ručke(korištene za promjenu veličine, "
"rotaciju, ...). Drške radijusa mijenjaju veličinu drški. Ako ih možete "
"povećati lakše ih je pogoditi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grab sensitivity"
msgstr "Dohvati osjetljivost"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "This option defines how exactly you need to hit a handle to select it."
msgstr "Ova opcija definira tačno kako morate udariti dršku da je selektujete."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Paste offset"
msgstr "Umetni pomak"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is only active if <guilabel>Paste at Cursor</guilabel> is disabled. If "
"you copy a shape with the shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> and paste it with <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo>, and do that at a place where already "
"a shape is this offset is used to paste the new shape to the bottom/right."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je aktivno samo kada <guilabel>Umetni kao kursor</guilabel> je "
"deaktivirano. Ako kopirate oblik sa prečicom <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> i umetnete sa <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo>, i uradite to na mjestu gdje već ima "
"oblik za ovaj pomak korišten za umetanje novog oblika na dno/desno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Paste at Cursor"
msgstr "Umetni na kursor"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Disables the paste offset and insert a pasted shape at the mouse cursor "
"position."
msgstr ""
"Deaktivira umetanje pomaka i ubacivanje umetnutog oblika na poziciju kursora."

#. Tag: title
#: options.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Grid</title>"
msgstr "<title>Rešetka</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: options.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Grid</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Rešetka</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: options.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Grid</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Rešetka</phrase>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Grid</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Rešetka</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show grid"
msgstr "Prikaži mrežu"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, &stage; will display a grid of dots representing the "
"intersections of imaginary horizontal and vertical lines. You can use these "
"dots to precisely position objects on the slide."
msgstr ""
"Ako omogućen &stage; će pokazati rešetku tački koje predstavljaju presjeke "
"imaginarnih horizontalnih i vertikalnih linija. Možete koristiti ove tačke "
"za precizno pozicioniranje objekata na slajdu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Snap to grid"
msgstr "Pripoj za mrežu"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is enabled, when dropping or moving objects on the slide the top "
"left corner of the object will <quote>snap</quote> or move, to the nearest "
"grid point."
msgstr ""
"Ako je ovo omogućeno, prilikom puštanja i micanja objekata na slajdu gornji "
"lijevi čošak objekta će <quote>šćepati</quote> ili se pomaći, ka najbližoj "
"tački na mreži."

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This does reduce your freedom to freely position objects on the slide, "
"however it also helps to line up objects precisely. It is easily disabled or "
"enabled with this option, allowing you the best of both worlds."
msgstr ""
"Ovo smanjuje slobodu za slobodno pozicioniranje objekata na slajd, međutim "
"pomaže u preciznom poravnanju projekata. Lako se deaktivira ili aktivira sa "
"ovom opcijom, dozvoljavajući vam najbolje od oba svijeta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grid color:"
msgstr "Boja rešetke:"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can change here the grid color which is black as default."
msgstr "Možete promijeniti boju rešetke koja je zadana kao crna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spacing"
msgstr "Razmak"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose to keep the same ratio for the two settings below by having "
"the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"link.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon or to separate the two "
"settings by using the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"break.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon."
msgstr ""
"Možete odabrati da držite isti omjer za dvije postavke ispod imajući "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"link.png\" format=\"PNG"
"\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> ikonu ili da ih odvojite u dvije "
"postavke koristeći <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"break.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> ikonu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Horizontal:"
msgstr "Horizontalno:"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the space in centimeters between two points on an horizontal line on the "
"grid. Default is 0.5 centimeter."
msgstr ""
"Postavi razmak u centimetrima između dvije tačke na horizontalnoj liniji "
"mreže. Zadani je 0.5 centimetara."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: options.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vertical:"
msgstr "Vertikalno:"

#. Tag: para
#: options.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the space in centimeters between two points on a vertical line on the "
"grid. Default is 0.5 centimeter."
msgstr ""
"Postavi razmak u centimetrima između dvije tačke na vertikalnoj liniji "
"mreže. Zadani je 0.5 centimetara."

